  "title": "How to change operator in currentRefinedValues widget. ",
  "body": "I can't change operator . I use transformdata but it doesn't work. \r\n\r\ntransformData: {\r\n          item(item) {\r\n            item.computedLabel = filterNameReplace(item.computedLabel);\r\n            item.operator = \"do\"; //test\r\n            console.log(item); //display item corectly\r\n            return item;\r\n          },\r\n        },\r\n\r\nfunction filterNameReplace(name){\r\n  name2 = name.toString();\r\n  name2 = name2.replace(\"≤\" , \"do\");\r\n  name2 = name2.replace(\"≥\" , \"od\");\r\n  return name2;\r\n}\r\n\r\nOn page still is \"≤\" but console.log(item) show me correct values. ",
